@using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Identity
@using SIGAE.Web.Data.Entities
@using SIGAE.Web.Helpers
@inject IUserHelper userHelper


<ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
    @if (userHelper.IsSigned(User))
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="ChangeUser">@this.User.Identity.Name</a>
        </li>
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Logout">Salir del sistema</a>
        </li>
    }
    else
    {
        <li class="nav-item">
            <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Login">Ingresar</a>
        </li>
    }
</ul>

